OL,3,CSwinney dismisses Starmer's claim
OL,4,Cquestions remain after Murrell
OL,5,Cembezzlement
OL,7,FSNP leader John Swinney has dismissed
OL,8,FKeir Starmer's suggestion that there
OL,9,Fwere "questions that need to be
OL,10,Fanswered" after the former chief
OL,11,Fexecutive Peter Murrell admitted
OL,12,Fembezzling just over #400,000 from the
OL,13,Fparty.
OL,15,FThe prime minister said people would
OL,16,Fbe "baffled" that people in charge of
OL,17,Fthe SNP "say they didn't know anything
OL,18,Fabout what was going on".
OL,26,@qD@FOUrD@IO]xD@DOUxD@LO]yD@IOUzD@XO]
