OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779891067
OL,3,CSwinney dismisses Starmer's claim
OL,4,Cquestions remain after Murrell
OL,5,Cembezzlement
OL,7,FHis comments came after former SNP
OL,8,Fleader, and one-time Scottish first
OL,9,Fminister, Nicola Sturgeon, said she
OL,10,Fhad "no knowledge or suspicion
OL,11,Fwhatsoever" that her then husband had
OL,12,Fused party money to pay for personal
OL,13,Fitems.
OL,15,FMurrell, 61, pleaded guilty on Monday
OL,16,Fto embezzling a total of #400,310.65
OL,17,Ffrom the SNP between August 2010 and
OL,18,FOctober 2022.
OL,26,@rD@EOUsD@KO]
