OL,3,CSwinney dismisses Starmer's claim
OL,4,Cquestions remain after Murrell
OL,5,Cembezzlement
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe cash was used to buy a range of
OL,13,Fitems, including: a motorhome, various
OL,14,Fluxury goods and two cars.
OL,16,FOther purchases included designer
OL,17,Fkitchenware, multiple pairs of shoes,
OL,18,Fexpensive pens and a #1,200 space
OL,19,Ftelescope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
