OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779891067
OL,3,CSwinney dismisses Starmer's claim
OL,4,Cquestions remain after Murrell
OL,5,Cembezzlement
OL,7,FAsked if SNP leader and Scottish First
OL,8,FMinister John Swinney had questions to
OL,9,Fanswer about the matter, Starmer said:
OL,10,F"I think anybody looking at what's
OL,11,Fhappening up in Scotland will be
OL,12,Fbaffled that those at the top of the
OL,13,FSNP say they didn't know anything
OL,14,Fabout what was going on, so clearly
OL,15,Fthere are questions that need to be
OL,16,Fanswered."
OL,18,FSwinney, however, said: "I don't
OL,19,Freally think I will be listening much
OL,20,Fto what Keir Starmer says about
OL,21,Fanything."
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@JO]zD@YOU}D@JO]
