OL,3,CSwinney dismisses Starmer's claim
OL,4,Cquestions remain after Murrell
OL,5,Cembezzlement
OL,7,FThe Scottish first minister said his
OL,8,Fparty's finances were "strong" and
OL,9,Fthat "strong and effective governance"
OL,10,Farrangements which he put in place
OL,11,Fafter becoming leader, two years ago,
OL,12,Fmeant supporters were still "donating
OL,13,Fsubstantially" to the party.
OL,15,FAs a result, he said, the party had
OL,16,Fspent "the best part of #1 million" on
OL,17,Fits recent Holyrood election campaign.
