OL,3,CSwinney dismisses Starmer's claim
OL,4,Cquestions remain after Murrell
OL,5,Cembezzlement
OL,7,FSome members raised concerns about
OL,8,Ffinances when Murrell was in place,
OL,9,Fwith former MP Joanna Cherry saying
OL,10,Fthat any questions that were asked
OL,11,F"were met with a brick wall".
OL,13,FBut, speaking on Tuesday, Swinney
OL,14,Finsisted that "these issues are in the
OL,15,Fpast", saying "the issues I have taken
OL,16,Fforward mean we have got good and
OL,17,Feffective governance".
